   content, how quickly the consumer satiates with one category and wishes
   to substitute it with another, and how the consumer trades off costly
   search efforts with selecting from a recommended list to discover new
   content. Taken together, these three elements allow us to characterize
   how an individual selects a diverse set of items to consume over the
